SELECT ? AS one FROM "blocks" WHERE "blocks"."account_id" = $? AND "blocks"."target_account_id" = $? LIMIT $?
SELECT ? AS one FROM "follows" WHERE "follows"."account_id" = $? AND "follows"."target_account_id" = $? LIMIT $?

SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" LEFT OUTER JOIN "mentions" ON "mentions"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" WHERE "statuses"."account_id" = $? AND ("statuses"."visibility" IN ($?, $?, $?) OR "mentions"."account_id" = $?) AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS ? AND "statuses"."reblog_of_id" IS ? GROUP BY "statuses"."id" ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
